# ERC-20 Token Contract

## Overview
A custom ERC-20 token built from scratch in Solidity without OpenZeppelin. Implements the full ERC-20 standard including transfer, approval and allowance mechanisms with gas optimization and custom errors.

## Contract
- ERC-20.sol — Core token contract

## Features
- Custom token name: JobToken (JBT)
- Transfer tokens between addresses
- Approve and transferFrom for delegated transfers
- Register members with token allocation
- Gas optimized with custom errors instead of require strings
- Events on every state change

## Tech Stack
- Solidity ^0.8.26
- Hardhat
- Ethers.js
- Chai

### Installation
npm install

### Run Tests
npx hardhat test

### Deploy
npx hardhat ignition deploy ignition/modules/ERC-20.js --network sepolia

## Deployed Contract
- Network: Sepolia Testnet
- Address: 0x212281278FC7f8f99F689Ae80d0269a7A01da08D
- Verified on: Etherscan - https://sepolia.etherscan.io/address/0x212281278FC7f8f99F689Ae80d0269a7A01da08D

## Test Coverage
17 tests passing covering:
- Register function access control
- Transfer validations and edge cases
- TransferFrom with allowance checks
- Approve function
- Event emission for all functions

